  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK721">
<l>vakaiyaṟintu vallavai vāycōrār colliṉ</l>
<l> tokaiyaṟinta tūymai yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The pure who know the classification of words having first ascertained the nature (of the court) will not (through fear) falter in their speech before the powerful body.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
